title: TrueCrypt 7.1a With CRC Hashs & Sources
description:
So TrueCrypt has been what is seems end of lifed. Either forces out of existence or just walking away from the table.


Each file has it's SHA256 or MD5 extra file listed here.  You can generate your own by using the portable or online via http://onlinemd5.com/.   You can use notepad to view .sha256 files. 

I have pulled it together because I think it is worth sharing, and getting it out there..  

Don't use BitLocker. ( https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BitLocker ) Closed source = NSA Hacked! SHOW ME THE CODE, Or I show you the door! :-)
